{"tid":2413970,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Whatsapp宣佈繼續推進受爭議私隱政策 堅持跟母企facebook分享用戶資料","createTime":"2021-02-19T05:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T11:37:14.000Z","uid":239336,"like":5,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"957bbf896a3efe55bab686ff8233fe264653d8e4","tid":2413970,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:42:39.000Z","msg":"雖然即時通訊軟件Whatsapp早前宣佈修改私隱政策，將會跟母公司Facebook分享用戶資料，引來極大反對及觸發社交移民，因而決定推遲修改。不過Whatsapp周四宣佈，將繼續推進這備受爭議的私隱政策。<br />\n<br />\nWhataspp表示，過去數周以來，聆聽到用戶不同的意見，了解他們對私隱的擔憂，因此現在決定繼續推行全新的私隱政策之餘，並會在程式中加入有關提醒橫幅，用戶可「按照自己的速度」來閱讀和同意條款。<br />\n<br />\n由於新修改令facebook及其他公司收集到用戶數據，包括其電號號碼及位置，引起全球廣泛的關注和反對，更令不少用戶「轉會」使用其競爭對手Telegram和Signal等。<br />\n<br />\n受到龐大的壓力後，Whatsapp當時一度決定把新修改推行的時間由2月推遲至5月，並強調這修改只是集中於商業方面的用途，讓用戶更容易跟企業聯繫，對私人對話的私隱度沒有影響，惟無阻仍有不少用戶棄用。<br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210219/4STIIB3ABRH5JIO5AR4YLNGAOI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210219%2F4STIIB3ABRH5JIO5AR4YLNGAOI%2F&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69IoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=3c5020bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210219%2F4STIIB3ABRH5JIO5AR4YLNGAOI%2F&h=a428d944\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210219/4STIIB3ABRH5JIO5AR4YLNGAOI/</a>"},{"pid":"bc441a161df8cc452ae8f0c27eacaa8a9817fd55","tid":2413970,"uid":83102,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:43:31.000Z","msg":"有冇人已經全面轉用signal?<br />\n除左工作群之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ba82ea2291d3235d064fb5ef8cc10f2fdde3cb","tid":2413970,"uid":254594,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bc441a161df8cc452ae8f0c27eacaa8a9817fd55","tid":2413970,"uid":83102,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T05:43:31.000Z","msg":"有冇人已經全面轉用signal?<br />\n除左工作群之外<img src=\"/a